  "prompt": "What is the meaning of sending nudge in hike messenger?",
  "response": "In Hike Messenger, a \"nudge\" is a feature that allows users to send a gentle reminder or prompt to someone in a chat. It can be used to draw attention to a message that hasn't received a response or to encourage the recipient to engage in the conversation. Essentially, it's a way to nudge someone to respond without sending a new message, serving as a friendly reminder. This feature is part of the app's focus on enhancing communication between users.",
